Using Cloudshark

CloudShark Interface: CloudShark provides an interface similar to Wireshark for online packet analysis.
Analysis Tools: It includes various analysis tools like 'Follow the Stream' and 'Threat Assessment' to evaluate network traffic and potential threats.
GeoIP World Map: This feature helps identify the geographic locations of endpoints in the network traffic.
Exporting Files: You can export packet capture files from CloudShark and analyze them further in Wireshark.



